The structure consists of 9 blocks in total.  There are 3 layers.  The base layer comprises three large orange cylindrical blocks.  On top of these pillars, two yellow rectangular blocks are placed side-by-side, forming a platform.  On top of the platform sits a vertical green rectangular block, topped by a curved yellow block (likely a cap). The structure is symmetrical with the two rectangular blocks forming a platform on the pillars.

* Block Index 10 (Yellow Rectangle) x 2
* Block Index 5 (Green Rectangle) x 1
* Block Index 14 (Yellow Curved/Half-Circle) x 1
